TI  - The detection and cure of breast cancer.
PG  - 667-84
AB  - The appropriate use of screening mammography can significantly decrease deaths 
      from breast cancer. Physicians and patients must become more vigilant in using 
      available diagnostic modalities if we are to improve upon the survival of 
      patients with breast cancer.
FAU - Potchen, E J
